data.description:
Looking for that perfect place in the country that has everything and more?? Look no further and welcome home to this renovated ranch on 2.5 acres!  4 Bedrooms, 2 full baths, 2 fireplaces, a massive detached garage with all the bells and whistles, a pole barn, 2 smaller barns, a fenced in yard and an expansive front and side yard with fruit trees and room for a garden!  All of this and close to Lake Michigan! 
This is truly a slice of heaven!  Call for your private tour today!!!
